<h2><a href="https://kottke.org/23/08/the-expressive-illustrations-of-felicia-chiao">The Expressive Illustrations of Felicia Chiao</a></h2>

<div class="meta">
<div class="author"><span class="pre-name">posted by </span><a href="http://www.kottke.org">Jason Kottke</a> <span class="timestamp"><i class="fa fa-clock-o" aria-hidden="true" style="font-weight:300;"></i>  Aug 07, 2023</span></div>
</div>



<div class="post">

<p><img src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODdhAQABAPAAAP///wAAACwAAAAAAQABAEACAkQBADs=" width="1000" height="1250" border="0" alt="illustration of two yellow figures sitting in red flowers" data-src="/plus/misc/images/felicia-chiao-23-01.jpg"></p>

<p><img src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODdhAQABAPAAAP///wAAACwAAAAAAQABAEACAkQBADs=" width="1000" height="1250" border="0" alt="illustration of several figures in patterned dress" data-src="/plus/misc/images/felicia-chiao-23-02.jpg"></p>

